name: Pokemon prism v0.95.0254 [GBC]
description:
Hello there!

Welcome to Pokemon Prism!

Pokemon Prism is one of an all time rom hack with new cities to walk around in, new Pokemon to find and catch, new caves and dungeons to explore, and much more!

There are 5 Regions:

Kanto,

Johto,

Naljo,

Rijon,

Tunod.

Pokemon Prism from 2020 is a hack of the english Pokemon Crystal from 2001, which is from the original japanese Pokemon Crystal made in 2000.

You can download Pokemon Prism for the Nintendo Gameboy Colour/Gameboy Advance or for the Nintendo 3DS.

Or you can scan the QR code with the FBI software on your Nintendo 3DS to download Pokemon Prism.

Tips: You need to have a hacked Nintendo 3DS to install CIA games off the Nintendo 3DS SD card.
